brown's body was found march 10 by firefighters who responded to a call at 3 a.m. at his apartment, according to monmouth county prosecutor john kaye
the body was found in the kitchen, kaye said. firefighters apparently removed the body, and it was not until the medical examiner's office detected gasoline on the clothes that an investigation began, leading to swain's arrest tuesday
