that too may pass without much disruption of stock prices, brokers say, but until it is over it adds an additional element of uncertainty for investors
meanwhile, the debate continues on wall street over whether the market is making a sustainable comeback from the crash last fall
the pessimists argue that stocks are merely enjoying a ``bear market rally'' that may not last much longer. but to date the optimists seem to have the upper hand
